text: Harald Platou (29 October 1877 - 23 September 1946) was a Norwegian lawyer and fencer. He competed in the individual épée event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1877 births Category:1946 deaths Category:Norwegian male fencers category:Norwegian lawyers Category:Olympic fencers of Norway Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Oslo
